{"tid":529070,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一屆] 全球性大學財力比較","createTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-14T15:24:46.000Z","uid":132968,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a6a04ee9d7ba218822222e1b4ae395659904c0","tid":529070,"uid":132968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-14T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/14/210703_c3836acf068a9b227834e0adda226ac2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F14%2F210703_c3836acf068a9b227834e0adda226ac2.jpg&h=6f2b6a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBy comparing the total funding and funding per student, we can see (in alphabetical order):<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A*</span></span>-tier<br />\nUniversity of Cambridge<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">A</span></span>-tier<br />\nNational University of Singapore<br />\nUniversity College London<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">B</span></span>-tier<br />\nHong Kong University of Science and Technology<br />\nThe Chinese University of Hong Kong<br />\nUniversity of Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">C</span></span>-tier<br />\nCity University of Hong Kong<br />\nHong Kong Polytechnic University<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Come on... HKSAR Government, our universities are seriously under-funded.<br />\n Make Hong Kong Great again please</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Source for Funding:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cuhk.edu.hk/bursary/eng/financial_info/1617_financial_report_cuhk.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cuhk.edu.hk%2Fbursary%2Feng%2Ffinancial_info%2F1617_financi